/**
 * Search override — intentionally empty.
 *
 * Pagefind is disabled (`pagefind: false` in astro.config.mjs), and the
 * prototype search affordance is the command palette opened from the
 * `#searchTrigger` box in the sidebar (rendered by the PageFrame override and
 * driven by docs.js). The default Starlight `<site-search>` dialog must not
 * render, so this override emits nothing and removes the default search UI and
 * its styling.
 *
 * Note: overriding `Search` (so it differs from the default component) is what
 * makes Starlight's Header attempt to render search even with Pagefind off —
 * but our Header override renders nothing, so no stray search markup appears.
 */
---
